Name: Donut or Cookie
About the game: Donut or Cookie is a side-view physics puzzle game. The player needs to toss a pink donut or cookie into the customer's bag. you can choose a donut or a cookie, they have 2 shapes, a circle and a square, this is actively used in solving puzzles. The game has 80 levels that become more difficult as you progress, new items are added to pass, complicating and diversifying the gameplay. I bet only 25% of people will complete all levels and only 1% will collect all 3 candies in each level. So if you are looking for challenging puzzles then welcome! welcome!
